{"tid":300481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賣淫「女」竟是男扮女裝　嫖客報復侮辱狂毆","createTime":"2017-06-28T02:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T11:24:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"869d87e3936bd6127b0f87d7da02687880f99678","tid":300481,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170628/photo/bkncn-20170628020753471-0628_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170628031506\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170628%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170628020753471-0628_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170628031506&h=bf2d0dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地近日瘋傳片段，一名男子疑因男扮女裝賣淫被揭發，結果遭到多名嫖客侮辱及毆打。事件惹起網民熱議，有人認為男子「活該」，但亦不少人狠批嫖客所為「太過份」，要求警方介入調查。 <br />\n<br />\n片段未有交待時間和地點。從片段所見，一名身穿藍色連身裙、頭戴假髮、腳踩高踭鞋的「女子」蹲在牆邊，被疑似是嫖客的人另外數人不停出言辱罵，更屢次動粗毆打下體。原來「女子」實際上是男子，相信是男扮女裝賣淫後被揭發，嫖客認為「貨不對辦」而找上門報復。男子不斷求饒「我對不起你哥哥」，但一眾嫖客都不為所動。 <br />\n<br />\n嫖客其後要求歸還已收取的「肉金」，又向男子索取賠償，「我跑成這樣，買瓶水喝不行呀？」；嫖客後來更喝令要男子脫光衣服，聲稱「別讓他害人」。 <br />\n<br />\n網民對片段的反應兩極，有人認為該男子男扮女裝賣淫，做法極不可取，有如此下場亦是「活該」；但更多網民批評，男子的行為固然不妥，但嫖客的做法亦有問題，「人家也是混口飯吃，至於這樣羞辱人家麼」、「覺得他好可憐，好無助」、「兩邊的人，沒一邊是好貨！」"},{"pid":"016fcc46c2415a8de0285a6510d990c8f02d1487","tid":300481,"uid":41655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"碌鳩已漸痕"},{"pid":"c649a46a7f7d26f70b27fcacad0ac35080df39a9","tid":300481,"uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6d4c7ba72d0a9b089da06af09ad5608868b963","tid":300481,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"拐子佬都係搵啖飯食啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9f742952fde53e483a5e93282904a5101311ef","tid":300481,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"又回帶&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"02fafd8e38dff5afdca0e8f14a89fadc631b171f","tid":300481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606f7b2c7fb33077f8159938534817f10293e662","tid":300481,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"支那雞都是假的!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3607a03621b139e4514c1b1f121eb9bbf743a9bb","tid":300481,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碌鳩已漸痕</blockquote><br />\n見到有鳩的雞入返一千蚊"},{"pid":"2527854d41d2da7fec34dfc677d7ed55cbe3ee16","tid":300481,"uid":57739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"you竟然是個boy!"},{"pid":"a59bd7ffc3f3835c34b3af4fde1d3f8b089072a6","tid":300481,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"其實交易左未？"},{"pid":"e145bc32d3eb2d26bcf4b4f945efb53e6555b56a","tid":300481,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"睇打格想都覺得樣衰，成個如花咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbb4bda9f0212b6934414c3e520588a75fd3019","tid":300481,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>碌鳩已漸痕</blockquote><br />\n見到有鳩的雞入返一千蚊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a784f82199dbf53d1d6310f914a02f6b17b0c2c2","tid":300481,"uid":27305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"有鳩的妖魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b12b3d9de16302f57be1306071ad8d7ff2707a","tid":300481,"uid":76632,